msgid ""
"Debian 7.0 (<em>wheezy</em>) was released May 4th, 2013. This new version "
"of Debian included various interesting features such as <url id=\"http://"
"www.debian.org/News/2011/20110726b\" name=\"multiarch support\">, several "
